snr = eaglecore.types.snr_db(1)
noised = eaglecore.noise.awgn(signal=original, snr=snr)

print('MAE : {}'.format(eaglecore.metrics.mae(original, noised)))
print('MSE : {}'.format(eaglecore.metrics.mse(original, noised)))

fig = matplotlib.pyplot.figure()
_ = matplotlib.pyplot.imshow(noised, cmap='gray')
